Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要點名了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 幫她回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有是也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我看小褲褲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我再點一次喔 天海?
