Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有是也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露褲褲特大量~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代點的人太多了啦 笨蛋!
